title: DDFP 436: Peyton's legacy and best free agent fits
itunes:title: DDFP 436: Peyton's legacy and best free agent fits
description:
Shek sits down with Handsome Hank, Gregg Rosenthal and Dan Hanzus to talk Peyton Manning’s legacy, NFL free agents and more. Is Manning better than Brady? Where will the premier free agents end up? Did Shek cry during Peyton’s retirement press conference? Find out more on DDFP.
